OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex will
OL,8,Fbegin a visit to Australia on Tuesday,
OL,9,Fwhich includes both charitable and
OL,10,Fcommercial engagements across
OL,11,FMelbourne, Canberra and Sydney.
OL,13,FIt is the couple's second visit to
OL,14,FAustralia. In October 2018, Harry and
OL,15,FMeghan marked their first official
OL,16,Froyal tour as a married couple,
OL,17,Flanding in Sydney to huge crowds.
OL,19,FNow, after eight years, the Sussexes
OL,20,Fare returning to Australia - and a lot
OL,21,Fhas changed since their last visit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
