PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FWhy are Harry and Meghan visiting
OL,8,FAustralia?
OL,10,FHarry and Meghan's office said the
OL,11,Ffour-day visit will "focus on mental
OL,12,Fhealth, community resilience, and
OL,13,Fsupport for veterans and their
OL,14,Ffamilies, alongside private meetings
OL,15,Fand special projects".
OL,17,FIt is understood that their privately
OL,18,Ffunded visit will not include general
OL,19,Fwalkabouts to meet the public.
OL,21,FWhat is on their itinerary?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
