SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FBeginning in Melbourne, the Duke and
OL,8,FDuchess will engage with organisations
OL,9,Fdelivering services to young people
OL,10,Fand vulnerable women, alongside a
OL,11,Fvisit to one of Australia's leading
OL,12,Fchildren's hospitals.
OL,14,FHarry and Meghan's office said the
OL,15,Fcouple will also "place particular
OL,16,Femphasis on the veteran community".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThe couple will join members of the
OL,8,FInvictus community on the water in
OL,9,FSydney Harbour, and in Canberra, Harry
OL,10,Fwill attend engagements at the
OL,11,FAustralian War Memorial.
OL,13,FHarry and Meghan also have engagements
OL,14,Fwith Movember and Australian mental
OL,15,Fhealth organisation Batyr.
OL,17,FBoth the Duke and Duchess will be
OL,18,Fspeaking at separate ticketed events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
