OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FDelegate tickets for the summit,
OL,8,Fhosted at Melbourne's Centrepiece
OL,9,Fconference venue, are available for
OL,10,F#525, with platinum tickets costing
OL,11,F#1,250 and a virtual ticket allowing
OL,12,Fon-demand access to Harry's speech
OL,13,Fcosting #260.
OL,15,FFinally, the visit will conclude at a
OL,16,Frugby fixture in Sydney between New
OL,17,FSouth Wales Waratahs and Moana
OL,18,FPasifika at the Allianz Stadium on
OL,19,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
