OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FIt is understood that the couple's
OL,8,Fchildren will not be accompanying them.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIs there any opposition to their trip?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
