OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FA petition on Change.org demanding "no
OL,8,Ftaxpayer funding or official support
OL,9,Ffor Harry and Meghan's private visit
OL,10,Fto Australia" arguing that "public
OL,11,Ffunds should not be used for private
OL,12,Fvisits", has attracted more than
OL,13,F45,000 signatures.
OL,15,FThe New South Wales Police Force said
OL,16,Fit would "conduct an operation to
OL,17,Fensure public safety is maintained
OL,18,Fduring the visit by the Duke and
OL,19,FDuchess of Sussex".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
