OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FHow will it compare to the Sussexes'
OL,8,Flast official visit to Australia?
OL,10,FThe Sussexes carried out an official
OL,11,Froyal tour to Australia in 2018, five
OL,12,Fmonths after their royal wedding.
OL,13,FMeghan's pregnancy with Prince Archie
OL,14,Fwas announced shortly after their
OL,15,Farrival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FHarry said in his autobiography that
OL,8,FMeghan "dazzled" crowds on the "hugely
OL,9,Fdemanding tour", but warned her she
OL,10,Fwas "doing too well" and "making it
OL,11,Flook too easy "like Diana, Princess of
OL,12,FWales.
OL,14,FIn his book Spare, published in 2023,
OL,15,Fhe wrote: "Everyone knew that Mummy's
OL,16,Fsituation went from bad to worse when
OL,17,Fshe showed the world, showed the
OL,18,Ffamily, that she was better at
OL,19,Ftouring, better at connecting with
OL,20,Fpeople, better at being 'royal', than
OL,21,Fshe had any right to be."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776161176
OL,3,CCharity work, rugby and #1,400 a
OL,4,Cticket events: The Sussexes' Australia
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FHarry's parents, Charles and Diana,
OL,8,Fvisited Australia with their recently
OL,9,Fborn son William on their first major
OL,10,Froyal overseas tour in 1983.
OL,12,FThe 21-year-old princess proved a big
OL,13,Fdraw with the Australian public, and
OL,14,Fthe royal tour was hailed as a success
OL,15,Fin promoting the monarchy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
